      <title>特朗普提名两人出任美国财政部高级职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-nominates-two-people-for-top-posts-at-the-us-treasury</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫向美国参议院发送的一份文件，彭博新闻社周二晚间审阅了该文件，该文件显示，唐纳德·特朗普总统已提名两人担任财政部的重要职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-nominates-two-people-for-top-posts-at-the-us-treasury</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划任命 Quintenz 为美国衍生品监管机构负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-plans-to-pick-quintenz-as-head-of-us-derivatives-regulator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫发送给国会山的一份文件（彭博新闻社审阅了该文件），唐纳德·特朗普总统计划选择安德森·霍洛维茨旗下 a16z 加密货币部门的政策主管布莱恩·昆滕兹 (Brian Quintenz) 领导商品期货交易委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-plans-to-pick-quintenz-as-head-of-us-derivatives-regulator</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 02:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯在菲律宾中期选举演讲中抨击中国和杜特尔特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/marcos-slams-china-duterte-in-philippine-midterm-election-pitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在开始为其参议员候选人竞选时大力抨击中国，使得与北京的海上争端成为五月至关重要的中期选举的核心议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/marcos-slams-china-duterte-in-philippine-midterm-election-pitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 02:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜抨击特朗普接管加沙计划的“篡位者”美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/north-korea-slams-usurper-us-over-trump-s-gaza-takeover-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜国家媒体谴责唐纳德·特朗普接管满目疮痍的加沙地带并控制格陵兰岛和巴拿马运河等其他领土的提议是侵略行为，称美国为一己私利侵犯其他国家权利的“篡位者”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/north-korea-slams-usurper-us-over-trump-s-gaza-takeover-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦指责特朗普允许对美国消费者实行“开放政策”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/warren-accuses-trump-of-allowing-open-season-on-us-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦批评唐纳德·特朗普和顾问埃隆·马斯克关闭消费者金融保护局，称他们实际上是在将国家的“金融警察”边缘化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/warren-accuses-trump-of-allowing-open-season-on-us-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与菲律宾军方首脑讨论扩大联合演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/us-philippines-military-chiefs-discuss-expanding-joint-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对持续的与中国的紧张关系，美国和菲律宾军事将领讨论了如何扩大联合演习的“范围和能力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/us-philippines-military-chiefs-discuss-expanding-joint-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 00:19:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议员称税务官未能解决数十亿英镑的欺诈行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/taxman-failing-to-tackle-billions-of-pounds-of-fraud-mps-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[议员们表示，英国税务机关可能严重低估了非法避税行为，且没有采取足够措施来解决这一问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/taxman-failing-to-tackle-billions-of-pounds-of-fraud-mps-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普顾问称澳大利亚正在“扼杀”美国铝市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/australia-is-killing-us-aluminum-market-trump-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的高级贸易顾问表示，澳大利亚正在“扼杀”美国铝市场，这可能会对澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯争取下个月生效的关税豁免的努力造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/australia-is-killing-us-aluminum-market-trump-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫禁止记者参加“美国湾”争端活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/white-house-bars-reporter-from-event-in-gulf-of-america-flap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，白宫禁止美联社记者报道总统唐纳德·特朗普和顾问埃隆·马斯克的活动，这家长期通讯社表示，此举是对其风格指南未采用总统新的“美国湾”标签的惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/white-house-bars-reporter-from-event-in-gulf-of-america-flap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:10:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赖特称美国应停止关闭燃煤电厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/us-should-stop-closure-of-coal-fired-power-plants-wright-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源部长克里斯·赖特表示，美国应该停止关闭燃煤发电厂，并补充说，未来几十年，燃煤燃料来源对国家电力系统至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/us-should-stop-closure-of-coal-fired-power-plants-wright-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 21:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
